items.name: Titanium Tank Chromatic Cardioid 2020
items.item_description: Thanks to the full spectrum of players like you, we'll conquer this pandemic, just like you conquered endless waves of murderous robots. Awarded to donors of Potato's MvM Server's charity tour!
